  Magnus smilied at the devices. Courage had done well. He had been in the 
science lab since they arrived. His bots flew off. They put each devise in a 
circle around the base. It started 40 miles out. So to give fair warning. 
Also it sent a jamming signal to disrupt a comm unkess on the coded frequency 
used by council members. The  devises where set and ready. They each dug 100 
feet under the ground. The dirt was covered over them and smoothed so not to 
be visibly seen. Then the  devices sent another jamming signal to  disrupt 
any scan that could pick them up. Magnus laughed as they came back. "This 
will help us exeptionaly."
